{"tid":2286439,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"胡定欣宣佈離開TVB！兩奪視后：來年以另一個模式帶來更多作品","createTime":"2020-11-15T04:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T05:08:01.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"341e25051d112c750e656910359599b85c79b545","tid":2286439,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:17:43.000Z","msg":"兩屆視后胡定欣休息一年後宣佈離開TVB，佢感謝喺無線一直以嚟幫佢嘅人，目前佢正在拍攝《白色強人2》，或會成為佢嘅告別作，胡定欣指會加入邵氏，來年以另一個模式帶來更多作品。<br />\n<br />\n胡定欣加入藝員訓練班，喺2003年出道，2015年中，於劇集《鬼同你OT》中飾演女鬼姜蓉（姜姐）一角，大獲好評，更喺2015年《萬千星輝頒獎典禮》中首奪「最佳女主角」。翌年，《城寨英雄》擔正女主角「刁蘭」，同陳展鵬嘅CP超受觀眾歡迎，成功「冧莊」再奪視后。<br />\n<br />\n不過近年拍劇數量大減，有傳佢將轉投古天樂公司旗下，又有指佢會同大台續約。胡定欣今日終於宣佈去向，佢表示將加入邵氏兄弟國際影業有限公司，展開合作。"},{"pid":"153d9dc47f4b8466f281cd00e32d5cebeb893b46","tid":2286439,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波"},{"pid":"a2d805478f02710e9a434b97b7a964509124cacd","tid":2286439,"uid":12621,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"邵氏咪又係tvb，不要分那麼細"},{"pid":"c7c7dca03ea401589e286ef34ec212be91dde27f","tid":2286439,"uid":205176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"仲留係入面既都是垃圾"},{"pid":"be36458a136f22a3e7624424e02360814217737a","tid":2286439,"uid":80503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092215_e8ece7157b849f6b742a98e8ca080f5f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092215_e8ece7157b849f6b742a98e8ca080f5f.gif&h=421888fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/2b0/7a7/2b07a770ce2771fe1648786c70df975d9da841b6_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F2b0%2F7a7%2F2b07a770ce2771fe1648786c70df975d9da841b6_n.jpg&h=32ff218d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e55f853ff87a3f6ecafccf6f8110143400fe41a0","tid":2286439,"uid":343229,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T05:01:21.000Z","msg":"佢啲戲唔算差 有時拎到好劇本好角色甚至做得幾好<br />\n不過真係冇主角相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咁多年主角都係妹仔相 又冇乜觀眾緣咁<br />\n反而做配角個陣好似仲受歡迎啲<br />\n同唐姨一樣（佢好戲過唐姨）<br />\n同以前姣佘 張可頤 宣萱 郭可盈呢啲真係差太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n李施嬅都有主角相過佢<br />\n但都好過依家呢班蔡思貝 江嘉敏呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做戲做到屎屙唔出咁款<br />\n可惜都老了"},{"pid":"63483d73d1d4280e2dce4d427edf1fb58c6e9896","tid":2286439,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"幾時出道拍av"}]}